# Laura's Python development environment

To use:
```
nix develop github:bgamari/laura-python-flake
```

To add this as a dependency of another project: In your `flake.nix`:
```nix
{
  inputs.laura-python-flake.url = "github:bgamari/laura-python-flake";

  outputs = { self, nixpkgs, laura-python-flake }: {
    devShells.x86_64-linux.default =
      laura-python-flake.devShells.x86_64-linux.default;
  };
}
```
